<h1>Audit (A-09-13-02035)</h1>

<h2>11-26-2013<br />
Noridian Healthcare Solutions, LLC, Inappropriately Paid Hospitals' Medicare Claims Subject to the Postacute Care Transfer Policy in Jurisdiction 2</h2>

<h2 class="line">Complete Report</h2>

